sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant CLI as contextos CLI
  participant Store as SQLite KB Store
  participant AI as AI Package
  participant OpenAI as OpenAI API

  User->>CLI: contextos docs generate retail-platform --force
  CLI->>Store: getRepositoryEvidence(repo)
  CLI->>AI: generateRepositoryDocumentation(evidence)
  AI->>AI: create deterministic Markdown from graph facts
  alt OPENAI_API_KEY set
    AI->>OpenAI: send compact repo graph evidence
    OpenAI-->>AI: explanatory onboarding Markdown
    AI-->>CLI: doc with LLM variant + deterministic variant
  else missing key or API failure
    AI-->>CLI: doc with deterministic variant only
  end
  CLI->>Store: saveRepositoryDoc(doc)

  loop service and endpoint targets
    CLI->>Store: getGraphItemEvidence(nodeId)
    CLI->>AI: generateGraphItemDocumentation(evidence)
    AI->>AI: create deterministic item doc
    alt OPENAI_API_KEY set
      AI->>OpenAI: send compact service/endpoint evidence
      OpenAI-->>AI: explanatory Markdown
    end
    CLI->>Store: saveGraphItemDoc(doc)
  end
